OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773951077
OL,3,CMultiple wildfires started
OL,4,Cdeliberately on Bodmin Moor
OL,6,FA number of wildfires on Bodmin Moor
OL,7,Fare believed to have been started
OL,8,Fdeliberately, the fire service has
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FCornwall Fire and Rescue Service said
OL,12,Ffirefighters attended multiple
OL,13,Fseparate wildfires which broke out on
OL,14,FWednesday, 18 March.
OL,16,FCrews and appliances from Bodmin,
OL,17,FWadebridge, Delabole, Launceston and
OL,18,FCallington were deployed to extinguish
OL,19,Fthe fires and stop them from spreading
OL,20,Fto nearby homes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
