OL,3,CMultiple wildfires started
OL,4,Cdeliberately on Bodmin Moor
OL,6,FOne of the blazes at Bolventor spread
OL,7,Facross hundreds of meters and left
OL,8,Flarge areas of scorched grassland.
OL,10,FThe force said: "Cornwall Fire and
OL,11,FRescue Service have attended multiple
OL,12,Fseparate wildfires today at different
OL,13,Flocations within Bodmin Moor.
OL,15,F"Appliances from Bodmin, Wadebridge,
OL,16,FDelabole, Launceston and Callington
OL,17,Fhave attended to fight the flames,
OL,18,Falongside officers with drones
OL,19,Fmonitoring the incident and preventing
OL,20,Fthe fire from spreading to nearby
OL,21,Fhomes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
