OL,3,CMultiple wildfires started
OL,4,Cdeliberately on Bodmin Moor
OL,6,F"Firefighters used beaters and hose
OL,7,Freels to extinguish the fires, and the
OL,8,Fcause is believed to be arson.
OL,10,F"Police have been informed and are
OL,11,Finvestigating."
